        </uncertainty>
        <comment xml:lang="en">Literature value (Statistics Canada, 2007 &amp; Shaffer, K.H., 2008, Consumptive water use in the Great Lakes Basin, USGS) (Vionnet, S., Quantis Water Database - Technical Report, 2012).</comment>
